      {
        "question": "Can I rent with a pet in Doncaster?",
        "answer": "Under Victorian law, landlords cannot unreasonably refuse a pet request. Doncaster is especially well-suited for pet owners due to its parks and walking trails. You must submit a written notice to your landlord, who has 14 days to respond. See our full [pets in rental guide](/guides/pets-rental-victoria) for details."
      }
